<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Attestation d'élevage — Poulets BF</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bf-green: #2E7D32;
      --bf-green-dark: #14532D;
      --bf-green-light: #E8F5E9;
      --bf-amber: #FF8F00;
      --bf-red: #CE1126;
      --bf-yellow: #FCD116;
      --ink: #0F172A;
      --ink-soft: #475569;
      --ink-muted: #94A3B8;
      --paper: #FFFFFF;
      --border-fine: #D1D5DB;
    }
    @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      width: 210mm; min-height: 297mm; margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--paper);
      font-family: 'Noto Sans', 'Inter', sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink); font-size: 10pt;
    }
    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 210mm; min-height: 297mm;
      padding: 12mm 15mm;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .page::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4mm;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--bf-red) 0%, var(--bf-yellow) 50%, var(--bf-green) 100%);
    }

    .header {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding-top: 6mm;
      padding-bottom: 5mm;
      border-bottom: 2pt solid var(--bf-green);
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }
    .brand strong { font-size: 18pt; color: var(--bf-green); font-weight: 700; }
    .brand span { display: block; font-size: 8pt; color: var(--ink-muted); }

    .doc-meta {
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 9pt;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
    }
    .doc-meta strong { color: var(--ink); font-size: 11pt; display: block; }

    h1 {
      font-size: 24pt;
      color: var(--bf-green-dark);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1mm;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 11pt;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }

    .profile-card {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
      gap: 6mm;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 6mm;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bf-green-light), #FFFFFF);
      border-radius: 3pt;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
      border: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
    }
    .avatar {
      width: 30mm; height: 30mm;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bf-green), var(--bf-amber));
      color: #FFFFFF;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 20pt;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .profile-info strong {
      font-size: 18pt;
      color: var(--bf-green-dark);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 1mm;
    }
    .profile-info p { font-size: 10pt; color: var(--ink-soft); }
    .badges { margin-top: 3mm; display: flex; gap: 2mm; }
    .badge {
      padding: 1mm 3mm;
      background: var(--bf-green);
      color: #FFFFFF;
      border-radius: 10pt;
      font-size: 8pt;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.3pt;
    }
    .badge.amber { background: var(--bf-amber); }

    .certify-text {
      font-size: 11pt;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      text-align: justify;
      padding: 0 4mm;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }
    .certify-text strong { color: var(--bf-green-dark); }

    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 4mm;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }
    .stat {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 5mm;
      background: #F9FAFB;
      border-top: 3pt solid var(--bf-amber);
    }
    .stat-value {
      font-size: 22pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--bf-green-dark);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 9pt;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.3pt;
      margin-top: 2mm;
    }

    .details {
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }
    .details h3 {
      font-size: 12pt;
      color: var(--bf-green-dark);
      margin-bottom: 3mm;
      padding-bottom: 1mm;
      border-bottom: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
    }
    .details dl {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3mm 8mm;
    }
    .details dt { font-size: 8pt; color: var(--ink-muted); text-transform: uppercase; }
    .details dd { font-size: 10pt; color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }

    .signature-zone {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
      gap: 8mm;
      align-items: end;
      margin-top: 12mm;
    }
    .sig-block {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 12mm;
      border-top: 1pt solid var(--ink);
    }
    .sig-block strong { display: block; font-size: 10pt; }
    .sig-block span { display: block; font-size: 9pt; color: var(--ink-soft); }

    .qr-block {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2mm;
      border: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
    }
    .qr-block img { width: 25mm; height: 25mm; display: block; }
    .qr-block span { display: block; font-size: 7pt; color: var(--ink-muted); margin-top: 1mm; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; }

    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 8mm; left: 15mm; right: 15mm;
      font-size: 7pt;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
      padding-top: 3mm;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <header class="header">
      <div class="brand">
        <strong>Poulets BF</strong>
        <span>FASO DIGITALISATION · Burkina Faso</span>
      </div>
      <div class="doc-meta">
        <strong>Attestation N° {{attestationId}}</strong>
        Émise le {{issuedAt}}
      </div>
    </header>

    <h1>Attestation d'élevage</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Preuve d'activité avicole enregistrée sur la plateforme souveraine Poulets BF</p>

    <section class="profile-card">
      <div class="avatar">{{initials}}</div>
      <div class="profile-info">
        <strong>{{eleveurName}}</strong>
        <p>{{region}} · Membre depuis {{memberSince}}</p>
        <div class="badges">
          {{#if halalCertified}}<span class="badge">Halal</span>{{/if}}
          {{#if bioCertified}}<span class="badge amber">Bio</span>{{/if}}
          {{#if vetVerified}}<span class="badge">Vétérinaire</span>{{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <p class="certify-text">
      Nous attestons que <strong>{{eleveurName}}</strong> est éleveur avicole actif
      enregistré sur la plateforme Poulets BF depuis <strong>{{memberSince}}</strong>.
      L'activité se déroule dans la région <strong>{{region}}</strong>. Le profil est
      vérifié, les transactions sont tracées et la réputation est conforme aux exigences
      de la plateforme souveraine FASO DIGITALISATION.
    </p>

    <section class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-value">{{totalSales}}</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Ventes totales</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-value">{{avgRating}}★</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Note moyenne</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-value">{{totalClients}}</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Clients servis</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="details">
      <h3>Détails éleveur</h3>
      <dl>
        <div><dt>Nom complet</dt><dd>{{eleveurName}}</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Région</dt><dd>{{region}}</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Commune</dt><dd>{{city}}</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Téléphone</dt><dd>{{phone}}</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Spécialités</dt><dd>{{specialties}}</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Capacité</dt><dd>{{capacite}} poulets</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Groupement</dt><dd>{{#if groupement}}{{groupement}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Dernière activité</dt><dd>{{lastActivityAt}}</dd></div>
      </dl>
    </section>

    <section class="signature-zone">
      <div class="sig-block">
        <strong>Éleveur</strong>
        <span>{{eleveurName}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="qr-block">
        <img src="{{qrCodeDataUri}}" alt="QR vérification">
        <span>{{attestationId}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sig-block">
        <strong>Plateforme</strong>
        <span>Poulets BF · FASO DIGITALISATION</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
      Document officiel généré le {{issuedAt}} · Valide 12 mois<br>
      Vérification en ligne : {{verificationUrl}}
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
